column2: SELECT SPhot.specObjID, SPhot.objID, S7.dr7ObjID, SObj.mjd, SObj.plate, SObj.fiberID, SObj.z, SObj.zErr, SObj.ra, SObj.dec, SObj.snMedian_u, SObj.snMedian_g, SObj.snMedian_r, SObj.snMedian_i, SObj.snMedian_z, SPhot.petroMag_u, SPhot.petroMag_g, SPhot.petroMag_r, SPhot.petroMag_i, SPhot.petroMag_z, SPhot.petroMagErr_u, SPhot.petroMagErr_g, SPhot.petroMagErr_r, SPhot.petroMagErr_i, SPhot.petroMagErr_z, gSL.h_alpha_eqw, gSL.h_alpha_eqw_err, ELP.EW_Ha_#, ELP.EW_Ha_#_Err INTO mydb.mytable_withEmission2 from dr1#.SpecPhoto AS SPhot JOIN dr1#.SpecObj AS SObj ON SObj.specObjID = SPhot.specObjID JOIN dr1#.galSpecLine AS gSL ON gSL.specObjID = SPhot.specObjID JOIN dr1#.SpecDR7 AS S7 ON S7.specObjID = SPhot.specObjID JOIN dr1#.emissionLinesPort AS ELP ON ELP.specObjID = SPhot.specObjID WHERE SObj.zWarning = # AND ELP.bpt = # AND SObj.snMedian_g > = #
